== 評價 ==
《權力的48條法則》成為一本暢銷書，除了在美國國內熱賣超過120萬本，還被翻譯為24種語言的譯本。<ref name=LATimes-in-house-guru/>《快速企業》雜誌形容本書為一本「如同宗教書籍般的經典」，《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》則稱讚該書的問世使得作者格林成為「嘻哈歌手、好萊塢菁英和在監囚犯共同仰慕的英雄式教主」。<ref name=LATimes-in-house-guru/><ref name="FastCompany">Johnson, Lynn. [http://www.fastcompany.com/1353390/50-cent-bible The 50 Cent Bible] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/1353390/50-cent-bible |date=20190608151139 }}. ''Fast Company''. 2009-09-10.</ref>

權力的48條法則據稱也是美國各監獄的圖書館中借閱率頗高的書籍之一<ref name=CNN/><ref>Garner, Dwight. [https://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/20/books/20book.html The Readers Behind Bars Put Books to Many Uses] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/20/books/20book.html |date=20210114163737 }}. [[紐約時報|''New York Times'']]. 2010-10-19.</ref>，美國一些大學也將此書列為一年級生必讀的書籍之一。<ref name=Millsaps>{{cite web|title=48 Laws of Power Syllabus|url=http://home.millsaps.edu/grubbmr/Management%20637%2048%20Laws%20of%20Power%20Summer%202010.pdf|publisher=Millsaps College|url-status=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110301213453/http://home.millsaps.edu/grubbmr/Management%20637%2048%20Laws%20of%20Power%20Summer%202010.pdf|archivedate=2011-03-01}}</ref><ref name=RamapoCollege>{{cite web|title=The 48 Laws of Power Syllabus|url=https://www.ramapo.edu/first-year/files/2013/03/12-25.pdf|publisher=Ramapo College|access-date=2020-09-14|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809070017/https://www.ramapo.edu/first-year/files/2013/03/12-25.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>知名饒舌歌手[[50_Cent|50 Cent]]表示自己深受這本書啟發，決定和作者格林接觸，兩人日後合作出版了《[[第50條法則|第50條法則]]》，《第50條法則》也成為格林第二本登上《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》年度[[紐約時報暢銷書榜|暢銷書榜]]的著作。<ref name=Guardian1>{{cite news|last=Burkeman|first=Oliver|title=When the gangsta rapper met the self-help guru|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/global/2009/sep/05/50-cent-robert-greene-interview|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2009-09-04|accessdate=2020-09-17|archive-date=2013-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728062221/http://www.guardian.co.uk/global/2009/sep/05/50-cent-robert-greene-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[巴斯達韻|巴斯達韻]]稱《權力的48條法則》使自己在職場上受益良多，更有能力應付有問題的電影製作人。<ref name="NewYorker"/>[[唱片騎師|唱片騎師]][[DJ普雷米爾|DJ普雷米爾]]深受書中第5條法則啟發，將「形象是權力的基石」（{{lang-en|Reputation is the cornerstone of power}}）的字眼[[刺青|刺青]]在自己的手臂上<ref name=OutlawCulture>{{cite news|last=Lee|first=Chris|title=Laws for an Outlaw Culture|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jul/12/entertainment/et-48laws12|newspaper=''LA Times''|date=2006-07-12|accessdate=2020-09-17|archive-date=2012-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016044449/http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jul/12/entertainment/et-48laws12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同樣為[[唱片騎師|唱片騎師]]的[[凱文·哈里斯|凱文·哈里斯]]身上也刺有第28條的精神「大膽行動」（{{lang-en|Enter with boldness}}）的刺青。<ref name=Calvinharris>{{cite web |first=Randy |last=Harris |title=calvin says: enter with boldness |url=http://thefmly.com/2011/05/31/calvin-says-enter-with-boldness/ |publisher=FMLY |accessdate=2011-05-31 |url-status= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609055600/http://thefmly.com/2011/05/31/calvin-says-enter-with-boldness/ |archivedate=2011-06-09}}</ref>《權力的48條法則》的內容也在[[UGK|UGK]]、[[杰斯|Jay-Z]]、[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]和[[德瑞克_(歌手)|德瑞克]]等流行音樂家的歌曲中被提及。<ref name="OutlawCulture"/><ref name=PrimeTime>{{cite web|title=Kanye West – Primetime Lyrics|url=http://rapgenius.com/Kanye-west-primetime-lyrics#note-312947|publisher=RapGenius|access-date=2020-09-17|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413033143/http://rapgenius.com/Kanye-west-primetime-lyrics#note-312947|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=LivingThisLife>{{cite web|title=UGK – Living This Life|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lsawMPR615E|access-date=2020-09-17|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212171613/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lsawMPR615E|dead-url=no}}</ref>
